*Voiced glottalized alveolar nasal 
*Voiced glottalized alveolar plosive 
*Voiced glottalized dental fricative 

====Restricted airstream====
*Creaky-voiced bilabial nasal
====Whispery voice====
*Breathy-voiced bilabial nasal 
*Breathy-voiced bilabial plosive 
*Breathy-voiced alveolar plosive 
*Breathy-voiced velar plosive 

